definition.value: A purine ribonucleoside 5'-monophosphate having guanine as the nucleobase.
A nitrile that is acetonitrile in which one of the hydrogens has been replaced by a p-chlorophenyl group.
An androstanoid having 17beta-hydroxy and 3-oxo groups, together with unsaturation at C-4-C-5..
Any D-aldose having a six-carbon chain with a phosphate group at C-6.
